                            <comment id="13089338" author="nehanarkhede" created="Tue, 23 Aug 2011 08:16:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;1. Fixed the shutdown bug by setting the closed queue flag before adding the shutdown command to the async producer queue&lt;br/&gt;
2. Added more logging at the trace level &lt;br/&gt;
3. Refactored the blocking async producer logic to use case match instead of nested if else&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13089888" author="junrao" created="Wed, 24 Aug 2011 00:18:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13089965" author="cburroughs" created="Wed, 24 Aug 2011 02:48:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IllegalQueueStateException was missed in the commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13090490" author="nehanarkhede" created="Wed, 24 Aug 2011 21:10:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;thanks for pointing that out. I checked it in now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
